Localisation-cUserLocalisedString.English: You are assembling a train in this yard on Siding 1. Your first task is to collect the blue then green TTA tanks from the Petroleum Yard 2 and 4. Check your 2D map and exit the yard when you are ready. You should be complete by 19:35.
Drop these back at the main yard in Siding 1. You will have some more wagons to add to these afterwards.
A timecheck of your progress so far has just been done. Finally you need to retrieve some HAA wagons from the coal sidings to the North and add them to the TTAs in Siding 1.
Wait briefly in Coal Shunt 2 while the wagons are given a final check.
You are given the go-ahead to shunt the HAAs back to the main yard. Couple them to the wagons already there to finish.
Good work. This shipment is ready to be hauled out shortly. Your evening shift is complete.
You finish your shift but did not complete all stages. Try again.
